summary: A beautiful Redguard who looks like a barbie doll !
descriptionHtml:
You start at Helgen during the dragon attack. No choice are made, no skills are improved => she is all yours !

Sorry guys, I didn\'t respect the Skyrim fluff when designing this one. This Redguard has no beautiful African features... She looks like your regular beach babe, barbie doll or **** actress ! She is nonetheless gorgeous and I hope you will enjoy playing with her.

To achieve the exact same result, you will have to use these mods :

Better Females by Bella 
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2812

My Type of Hair by Meister falls off cliff
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=6173

And to be sure to miss nothing ;) =>

Calientes Female Body Mod Big Bottom Edition -CBBE- 
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666

You\'re all set.
author: Eoloe
